    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered with regular detailing. Honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
