    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a breathtaking 2019 BMW M4 Heritage Edition in iconic Laguna Seca Blue. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with a full-body paint protection film (PPF) applied since day one; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The interior is equally remarkable, featuring Silverstone/Black Merino leather with M-color stitching that remains taut and free of any wear or creasing. It still retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by BMW master technicians. Every system\u2014from the adaptive M suspension to the Harman Kardon surround sound\u2014operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This M4 has never been tracked, never seen rain, and has been driven only on fair-weather weekends. The sale includes all original documentation, two keys, the original window sticker, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in turn-key, investment-grade condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
