      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in showroom condition both aesthetically and mechanically. Every surface reflects a commitment to preservation, offering the discerning buyer an opportunity to acquire a pre-owned vehicle that effectively mirrors its original delivery state. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its impeccable status.",
