      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've kept it garage-protected and pampered since day one, so you're getting a ride that's basically flawless. If you've been looking for that 'brand new' experience without the brand new price tag, you've found it! I'd love for you to come by and see how beautiful it is in person\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
