    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering. This example features the iconic 13B-REW twin-sequential turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting exceptional compression and a seamless transition between primary and secondary boost phases. The five-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement with zero grinding in the lower synchros. Its chassis retains the factory-specified double-wishbone architecture, providing unparalleled feedback through the communicative rack-and-pinion steering. Finished in its original configuration with a functional Torsen limited-slip differential and heat-cycle-managed cooling system, this FD represents a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
